hopobject.body: Yes, I play the guitar dapovar in australia It's all a sign that the Pebble Beach Concours, the greatestclassic car show on earth, is going plebian, although that's arelative term in this rarified setting. Tickets to Sunday's bigshow cost $225 in advance and $275 at the door. Some classiccars will fetch millions of dollars at pre-show auctions;Gooding & Co is estimating more than $3 million for a 1948 AlfaRomeo 6C 2500 Competizione roadster. Vintage California winesflow freely at the myriad parties and receptions leading up toSunday's show.
